whatever I want to say.

283
00:11:15,589 --> 00:11:17,489
Shut your mouth.

284
00:11:17,491 --> 00:11:19,224
Now, you are not
going to turn pro,

285
00:11:19,226 --> 00:11:21,460
and you are not going
to continue down this path,

286
00:11:21,462 --> 00:11:25,897
