292
00:11:37,644 --> 00:11:38,944
You sure?

293
00:11:38,946 --> 00:11:40,579
Your job was to keep track
of that one thing.

294
00:11:40,581 --> 00:11:41,746
Nice work.

295
00:11:41,748 --> 00:11:43,482
