the best way that I know how.

374
00:15:04,951 --> 00:15:06,685
Allison Holt is gonna
figure out what happened.

375
00:15:06,687 --> 00:15:08,253
And when she does,
her priority's not going to be

376
00:15:08,255 --> 00:15:09,821
