392
00:16:12,139 --> 00:16:13,839
You weren't supposed
to interfere.

393
00:16:13,841 --> 00:16:16,642
Neither were you.
How did you even know?

394
00:16:16,644 --> 00:16:17,943
She's not supposed
to tell you anything.

395
00:16:17,945 --> 00:16:19,979
She was forced to tell me

396
00:16:19,981 --> 00:16:21,947
when I got served
with this goddamn subpoena.

397
00:16:21,949 --> 00:16:23,349
You didn't want
to put them on the defensive,

398
00:16:23,351 --> 00:16:25,084
which is good,
because what you've just done

399
00:16:25,086 --> 00:16:26,318
