00:16:30,324 --> 00:16:32,925
because Travis Tanner is gonna
depose them under oath.

403
00:16:32,927 --> 00:16:34,927
Nobody here knows
a thing about that goddamn memo.

404
00:16:34,929 --> 00:16:36,261
Let them waste
their time with it.

405
00:16:36,263 --> 00:16:38,998
This is why you hire
outside counsel.

406
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,265
You can't see
how reckless that was,

407
00:16:40,267 --> 00:16:42,167
even now, after
it's blown up in your face.

408
00:16:42,169 --> 00:16:45,304
Fine, if you insist on
pre-deposing their depositions,

409
00:16:45,306 --> 00:16:47,573
let's get it over with.
You can start with me.

410
00:16:47,575 --> 00:16:50,042
