416
00:17:02,256 --> 00:17:04,456
but your father,
he's just trying to protect you.

417
00:17:04,458 --> 00:17:06,125
Yeah, look, I know
what he thinks he's doing.

418
00:17:06,127 --> 00:17:08,927
Marco, it's a year
and eight months.

419
00:17:08,929 --> 00:17:10,763
